  "analyst_note": "Jenkins January 2019 advisory: Multiple Groovy sandbox escapes allowing arbitrary code execution on the Jenkins controller from pipeline scripts. CVEs include CVE-2019-1003000 (Script Security Plugin), CVE-2019-1003001, CVE-2019-1003002. Any Jenkins user with Job/Configure permission can escape the sandbox. X-Jenkins header reveals version. Fixed: LTS 2.150.2, weekly 2.160. Also requires Script Security Plugin >= 1.50.",
